{"tid":555061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿選手未有獲贈三星手機  伊朗召見南韓大使抗議","createTime":"2018-02-09T05:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T06:30:19.000Z","uid":5195,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7cb382180427a98216e9e29666a2e93567b41ae4","tid":555061,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T05:50:28.000Z","msg":"南韓平昌冬奧參賽選手可以獲贈一部最新款三星手機作為禮物，但伊朗選手被排除在外。為此，伊朗召見南韓大使後，終獲允贈予手機。而北韓選手也將獲贈手機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　三星最新款智能手機奧運版Galaxy Note 8一部價值一千一百美元（約八千六百港元），共有四千部將送給平昌冬奧選手，但伊朗和北韓選手排除在外，因為這兩個國家遭到國際制裁。<br />\n<br />\n　　伊朗國營通訊社（IRNA）引述伊朗外交部發言人卡塞米的談話報道，南韓大使已被告知，「如果三星對其不智行為不道歉，將會嚴重影響三星和伊朗的貿易關係」。<br />\n<br />\n　　三星表示，其公司對此沒有評論，因為奧運發放禮物是由國際奧會（IOC）負責。平昌冬奧主辦單位也說，國際奧會負責發放手機。國際奧會其後表示，伊朗和北韓的選手都會獲贈手機，但北韓選手會被要求不要把手機帶回北韓。"},{"pid":"11a55a50e0ddac0e447bdaa560616acb026b5e57","tid":555061,"uid":33868,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T05:51:38.000Z","msg":"北韓選手會被要求不要把手機帶回北韓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe5e340e79f521254bb92dcedc66cd36090cbe0","tid":555061,"uid":22999,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T05:51:47.000Z","msg":"炸彈送都唔撚要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85685d382d3bd33c7c345bb21dae26baf789bae","tid":555061,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"dfe5e340e79f521254bb92dcedc66cd36090cbe0","tid":555061,"uid":22999,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T05:51:47.000Z","msg":"炸彈送都唔撚要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T05:58:35.000Z","msg":"驚伊朗真係攞去當炸彈用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7edb7b8f57d1a06f124ba686c6358831421e8ca1","tid":555061,"uid":43009,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T05:59:45.000Z","msg":"大種乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n召見人地大使R部手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8acf35aa7713a010c948f8fb65bb67cdbcabd4b","tid":555061,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11a55a50e0ddac0e447bdaa560616acb026b5e57","tid":555061,"uid":33868,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T05:51:38.000Z","msg":"北韓選手會被要求不要把手機帶回北韓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T06:22:00.000Z","msg":"即放囉"},{"pid":"56d96efecfede865daed09fc733aab90859bfda7","tid":555061,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T06:25:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>北韓選手會被要求不要把手機帶回北韓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>即放囉</blockquote><br />\n帶外國錢入境⋯又⋯<br />\n賣完機要即買野先得。"},{"pid":"d541be72c1dc334ac7162c9d0817cba96d537eed","tid":555061,"uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c8acf35aa7713a010c948f8fb65bb67cdbcabd4b","tid":555061,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11a55a50e0ddac0e447bdaa560616acb026b5e57","tid":555061,"uid":33868,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T05:51:38.000Z","msg":"北韓選手會被要求不要把手機帶回北韓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T06:22:00.000Z","msg":"即放囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T06:30:19.000Z","msg":"應該會有人主動r佢地放機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}